      "industries.hero.lede": "Builtly's primary customer is the engineering consultancy — the firms that produce signed, regulated deliverables. The platform's automated tiers are also bought directly by the buyers consultancies serve: real-estate developers, lenders, asset managers and the public sector. <span class=\"serif\">One platform. Multiple routes to market.</span>",
