      "about.hero.h1": "Created by entrepreneurs.<br/>Built by engineers.<br/>For engineers.",
      "about.insight.quote": "“Builtly provides the starting point. <span class=\"accent\">The engineer provides the engineering.</span>”",
      "about.hero.lede": "Builtly Engineering is the convergence of three rare disciplines under one roof: professional engineering accountability, capital-markets experience from real estate, and modern software development. <span class=\"serif\">It is not coincidental. It is the prerequisite.</span>",
