      "careers.hero.h1": "Build the platform<br/>engineering needs.",
      "careers.hero.lede": "Builtly is a small, deliberate team rebuilding the production layer of consulting engineering. The work is technically demanding, professionally accountable, and unusually consequential. <span class=\"serif\">We hire for judgment, depth and the long horizon.</span>",
