      "index.pipe.smark.tag": "From raw data to signed deliverable",
      "index.pipe.h2": "The pipeline.",
      "index.pipe.lede": "A processing pipeline where each stage is built to do one thing properly. Geometry and physics are deterministic. AI operates under regulatory constraint. Engineering judgment signs. End-to-end traceability — every claim can be rolled back to the source data behind it.",
      "about.seat.role.director": "Director",
      "about.seat.status": "— Composition under construction",
