      "plt.found.compute.p": "Geometry, statics and physical calculations run as deterministic numerical code, not stochastic AI output. Reproducible inputs produce identical outputs.",
      "plt.found.bim.p": "Native handling of IFC4, BCF 2.1 and engineering-format inputs through industry-standard libraries. Round-trip compatibility with BIM tools the engineering market already uses.",
      "plt.found.geo.p": "Direct integration with geospatial data, cadastral registers and authority interfaces. The platform reads what regulators publish — the integration is engineered, not improvised.",
      "plt.found.regpack.p": "Building codes, planning law and engineering standards expressed as machine-readable rule sets. Updates propagate to every module simultaneously, with version-stamped audit trail.",
