      "sec.steinan.lede": "A 9-storey residential building. <b>1,070 walls, 566 doors, 263 windows</b> across PLAN 00 to PLAN 06, plus a half-mezzanine at PLAN 05-A. The platform reads every storey in milliseconds — separating levels, mapping elevations, classifying elements. Below: each floor's complexity, revealed level by level.",
