      "dash.h2": "From engine output<br/>to commercial decision.",
      "dash.lede": "Every Builtly run produces more than engineering numbers. The same kernel that signs the structural calculation feeds a project-level decision view — material savings, regulatory compliance, market benchmarks and the carbon ledger, in one place. The engineer signs the technical work. Everyone else — board, lender, developer — gets the consolidated picture.",
