        "industries.s02.lede": "Some modules can be used directly by the organisations that need an early technical basis: developers testing a site, lenders screening risk, asset managers reviewing a portfolio and public agencies preparing procurement. When the risk or regulatory use requires it, the workflow moves into engineer review or consultancy-led delivery.",
